data.description:
NEW PRICE, Best priced pool home in community! WHY WAIT TO BUILD? 3 bed, 3 bath PLUS pool home in Harbor West, gated community in South Gulf Cove. Popular Lennar Venice floorplan, built in 2021, with impact glass in windows/sliders means lower insurance and less maintenance costs.

Open and flexible floorplan with 3 beds, 3 full baths and lots of storage! Spacious bedrooms with master suite including two walk-in closets, dual sinks in bathroom and oversized walk-in shower. Granite in kitchen and both bathrooms. Stainless appliances in kitchen, which features large island overlooking dining room and family room, perfect for entertaining. Corner pantry and white cabinets provide plenty of storage. No carpet, oversized diagonal tile throughout home.

One of the largest lots in community with water view at front and back of home. Enjoy morning sunrise from covered porch or sunsets from lanai! Pool area features pavers, spa integrated into pool and cage was replaced after Hurricane Ian with full 3-side panoramic screens, to make the most of water views. Minimal damage from Hurricane Ian, repairs completed.

For VA buyers, owners loan is transferrable with low interest rate!

Discover Harbor West, newer gated community within South Gulf Cove. Small, friendly community with some homes on boatable water, all homes overlooking lake or canal and community mailbox area to meet your neighbors. 2 access gates provide easy access for residents. Beautiful homes with tile roofs, landscaping and low HOA fee which includes lawn maintenance.

Close proximity to Englewood, Boca Grande, Port Charlotte and North Port with Wellen Park dining and activities including Braves Spring Training. Beaches at Englewood, Manasota Key and Boca Grande are all in easy reach along with restaurants, shopping, cycle trails and multiple golf courses including Rotonda West Country Club with 99 holes of golf. This is one of the best kept secrets - fast growing area which still retains small town charm.
